---
// Booking CTA Component - Bilingual
---

<section class="py-20 bg-kailash-dark text-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">
      准备好开始您的朝圣之旅了吗？
    </h2>
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
      Ready to Begin Your Pilgrimage?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-white/70 mb-8" data-lang-content="zh">
      2026年，让我们一起踏上这段改变生命的旅程
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl text-white/70 mb-8" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
      In 2026, join us on this life-changing journey
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/booking" class="bg-kailash-gold text-kailash-dark px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-kailash-accent transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <span data-lang-content="zh">立即预订</span>
        <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Book Now</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white/30 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition">
        <span data-lang-content="zh">联系我们</span>
        <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Contact Us</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-8" data-lang-content="zh">
      早鸟优惠：2025年12月31日前预订享受9折优惠
    </p>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-8" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
      Early Bird: 10% off for bookings before Dec 31, 2025
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
